snippet.title: Park Beyond — Beyond the Skies of Arabia Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Patch 4.0 is here for Park Beyond! The next major DLC update, Beyond the Skies of Arabia, is also available now!
🎢 New Track Types
🌌 New Flat Rides
👨‍🔧 New Entertainers
🗺️ New Maps
🏰 New Building Prefabs and Decorative Items
✨ and more
